Class Operator

java.lang.Object
operators.Operator
Direct Known Subclasses:
AddOperator, DivOperator, EqualOperator, ExpOperator, LeftParOperator, MultOperator, RightParOperator, SubtOperator
public abstract class Operator extends Object
The Operator class represents an abstract mathematical operator (e.g., addition, subtraction, multiplication, division).

Each operator has an associated precedence level, which determines the order in which operations are performed during expression evaluation. Higher precedence operators are evaluated before lower precedence operators.
